  "body": "# Features\n✔️Textures of saplings in inventory are now changed to corresponding tree seed\n\n![Camparison](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/eb8eb412bef5eb9d56f23507df572163d194fc28.webp)\n\n✔️Saplings on the ground are looking just the same\n\n✔️Names of the saplings are changed to \"Seed\" (English)\n\n🎨Compatible with most other resource packs\n\n![Camparison](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c381db2b34536d39b406689e43189dfef6a85070.webp)\n\nCredits to ferreusveritas owner of Dynamic Trees mod for beautiful textures :3\n(https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/dynamictrees The resource pack in under MIT licence because it uses textures from \"Dynamic Trees\" mod!)\nIf you have feedback or request write them in the comments and I will try to help you.\n",
